---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const updated = new Date(2026, 4, 1); // May 2026
const updatedLabel = updated.toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long' });
---

<PageLayout title="Now" description="What Théo Alessandro Hermann is focused on this month.">
  <section class="page-wrap now">
    <header class="now-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Now</span>
      <h1 class="now-title">May 2026 · Rio</h1>
      <p class="now-meta mono-caption">Updated {updatedLabel}</p>
    </header>

    <div class="now-body prose">
      <p>
        Two papers in motion. The Amsterdam tree-shade study went to
        <em>Nature Cities</em> this week. The favela morphology paper — LiDAR, CFD airflow, solar exposure
        — is the next submission, targeting June.
      </p>
      <p>
        Robotics side: building an open VLA benchmark on lerobot. Public release end of June.
        Reading recent world-model work in parallel.
      </p>
      <p>
        Building two stealth apps with shipping deadlines in May and June. Not yet linked from this
        site. Separate from
        <strong>Azimuth</strong>, an AI infrastructure agency launching alongside — kept under its
        own brand.
      </p>
      <p>
        Open to senior research and engineering conversations at frontier AI labs, and to a small
        number of consulting engagements at the intersection of built environment and AI
        infrastructure.
      </p>
      <hr />
      <p class="now-attribution">
        <a href="https://sive.rs/nowff" rel="noopener">/now page</a>, after Derek Sivers. Monthly
        refresh.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .now {
    padding-block: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem) var(--space-section);
  }
  .now-head {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .now-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    line-height: 1.08;
  }
  .now-meta {
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
  }
  .now-body {
    max-width: 60ch;
  }
  .now-body p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .now-attribution {
    font-size: 0.9rem !important;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted) !important;
  }
</style>
